data.description: You won’t want to miss this gorgeous, updated home! This home has the perfect blend of farmhouse finishes, character, & charm. The main floor of this raised ranch features a spacious living room which flows into the dining room. The dining room has plenty of room for a full size dining suite and also has access to the large deck. The beautiful kitchen has an abundance of cabinets and is open to the dining room for a perfect entertaining space. Also on the main level, there are 3 generously sized bedrooms including a large master bedroom with a full master bath, and an additional updated full bath. The finished basement adds an entire additional level of living space. The 1.6 acre private yard is pure fun for family and friends with a large above ground pool and a sprawling deck to gather with friends. Enjoy the sunrise from your front porch with the breath-taking view. Equipped with 2 wells - never run dry! Close to schools, restaurants, and Route 28!
